    {
        "author_association": "MEMBER",
        "body": "I'm going to lock this conversation because a lot of people will ask for this while we cannot provide support due to the IE11 support. Providing a solution with functions like `try-darken` could help us out, but we'll overcomplicate our codebase too much to make this possible. Maintaining this & tackling all edge cases will slow us down.\r\n\r\nWe 'll definitely have a look at support for css variables in the future (`v6`), but for now we 'll pass on this and focus on improving & extending other Bootstrap functionality.",
